This roll bundles a collection of Biology packages: blat, bowtie, bwa,
GenomeAnalysisTK, samtools, soapdenovo, and velvet.  To install, execute these
instructions on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a frontend), starting in
this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll biotools
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll biotools | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs individual environment
module files for each tool in /opt/modulefiles/applications.
